    "name": "Bashful Adoration",
    "steam_appid": 3017130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/d7bbe1380d8717d984c291f033bad024.avif?t=1759395072\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras_big/d7bbe1380d8717d984c291f033bad024.avif?t=1759395072 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/7c494e1cafc9779ad40cc6d9a719715d.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/7c494e1cafc9779ad40cc6d9a719715d.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/7c494e1cafc9779ad40cc6d9a719715d.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a Witch-filled 3D Platforming adventure! Harness the power of your broom to fly, skate and <strong>BASH</strong> through dangerous, magical environments (and gain the adoration of your crush!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/cd8ecc37287e6683f9f6b4f990313281.avif?t=1759395072\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras_big/cd8ecc37287e6683f9f6b4f990313281.avif?t=1759395072 width=800 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Four witches with clashing personalities, all trying to find love within complicated stages of       their lives</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A fantastical, magic world to discover, set on Sky-Islands, Magic Schools and more</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A dangerous and diverse cast of enemies to battle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Just the right amount of chaotic fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also included are fast paced, casual PvP battle modes where you must brawl it out with your rivals in order to gain the adoration of your crush! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your skills, brain and of course your heart as you engage in- </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/8d930c1bae820863ee9551b7f95590f8.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/8d930c1bae820863ee9551b7f95590f8.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/8d930c1bae820863ee9551b7f95590f8.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/6e681976706aaa2067f81321cd4d801e.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/6e681976706aaa2067f81321cd4d801e.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/6e681976706aaa2067f81321cd4d801e.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bash your opponents away from your crush, and charge up your swing to send them flying into the horizon</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New to fighting games? Not a problem! Easy to learn with space for mastery, everyone has the power to fight for their love!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/5e8b2323a7e42a2281c940842f0c6ef5.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/5e8b2323a7e42a2281c940842f0c6ef5.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/5e8b2323a7e42a2281c940842f0c6ef5.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/3deedef50449529723842da5317a8b45.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/3deedef50449529723842da5317a8b45.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/3deedef50449529723842da5317a8b45.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse the map from above, or get back into the fight in a flash, using your trusty broom! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free flowing, unrestricted movement lets players have complete control and adds a unique twist to the arena fighter genre</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/cdb775e78215f6d19e3b2978f42607fd.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/cdb775e78215f6d19e3b2978f42607fd.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/cdb775e78215f6d19e3b2978f42607fd.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/8c2f519668602f4af8a5325daeb11934.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/8c2f519668602f4af8a5325daeb11934.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/8c2f519668602f4af8a5325daeb11934.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything you see in the environment can be smacked around and hit into your rivals and enemies! Bushes, trees, almost anything can become a quick, make-shift projectile!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/28f5bdad0421bb9b2ccbb508ab7d8410.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/28f5bdad0421bb9b2ccbb508ab7d8410.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/28f5bdad0421bb9b2ccbb508ab7d8410.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/eed14a816654c5ce1c94d0c0c9b42fe3.poster.avif?t=1759395072\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/eed14a816654c5ce1c94d0c0c9b42fe3.webm?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017130/extras/eed14a816654c5ce1c94d0c0c9b42fe3.mp4?t=1759395072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from four distinct and competitive witches, and express yourself with a variety of unlockable skins, brooms and other cosmetics!</p>",
